    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892740/extras/2dae7cfaab46476705b8fd66e0100de1.poster.avif?t=1761220668\" width=700 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892740/extras/2dae7cfaab46476705b8fd66e0100de1.webm?t=1761220668\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892740/extras/2dae7cfaab46476705b8fd66e0100de1.mp4?t=1761220668\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>About</strong></h2>Deaf Wish has the typical characteristics of an old school japanese Horror RPG with its focus on puzzle solving and dealing with emotional trauma.<br><br>You'll play as Lily, a young girl who lost her father at an early age and who's mother became unstable because of it.<br>The gist of the game is that during day-phases you'll encounter reoccurring problems in Lily's life which you'll then process in her dreams.<br><br>Since the game is in its Early Access Stage only 1/3 of the story is currently playable.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>No real audio during day-phases to emphasize with Lilys condition<br></li><li>Slight horror with its focus on story.<br></li><li>Bloody and implicit scenes.<br></li><li>Physical save points (interaction with a blue teddy to save)<br></li><li>Controller Support<br></li><li>Puzzle solving<br></li><li>Detailed chase mechanic</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892740/extras/2d56db3f89e398d40c447dd9b2acf94c.poster.avif?t=1761220668\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892740/extras/2d56db3f89e398d40c447dd9b2acf94c.webm?t=1761220668\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1892740/extras/2d56db3f89e398d40c447dd9b2acf94c.mp4?t=1761220668\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
